Felix Knight https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Felix_Knight 0 William Felix Knight (stage name: Felix Knight, November 1, 1908 – June 18, 1998), was an American tenor, actor, and vocal teacher, best known for his role as Tom-Tom in the 1934 Laurel and Hardy musical film Babes in Toyland.
